1
00:00:01,421 --> 00:00:02,672
Did you hear that rumor?

2
00:00:02,923 --> 00:00:03,548
Huh?

3
00:00:05,592 --> 00:00:08,720
They say Managing Director Seo Yeong-woo's younger brother is taking his place.

4
00:00:10,347 --> 00:00:13,016
Wait, did Director Seo have a sibling?

5
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:18,813
A half-brother.

6
00:00:19,439 --> 00:00:19,940
Really?

7
00:00:20,732 --> 00:00:21,608
Yeah...

8
00:00:21,608 --> 00:00:22,359
And apparently...

9
00:00:22,359 --> 00:00:24,611
that brother exposed the corruption this time

10
00:00:24,611 --> 00:00:26,780
just to completely push his hyung out.

11
00:00:27,072 --> 00:00:28,573
Ah...

12
00:00:28,782 --> 00:00:30,158
It's a full-on family feud.

13
00:00:30,158 --> 00:00:31,201
Exactly.

14
00:00:31,785 --> 00:00:32,994
That's why Manager Kwon...

15
00:00:32,994 --> 00:00:34,037
He was on Director Seo's side.

16
00:00:34,037 --> 00:00:35,914
So that's why things turned out like this.

17
00:00:43,171 --> 00:00:44,589
Hello.

18
00:01:10,281 --> 00:01:11,241
Who are you?

19
00:01:11,241 --> 00:01:12,867
Why didn't you show up yesterday?

20
00:01:13,618 --> 00:01:15,370
Because you didn't listen to me.

21
00:01:16,579 --> 00:01:17,205
What?

22
00:01:18,373 --> 00:01:20,458
That Seo Yeong-woo ordered it,

23
00:01:20,458 --> 00:01:21,668
why didn't you report that?

24
00:01:23,378 --> 00:01:24,879
Because it isn't true.

25
00:01:27,132 --> 00:01:28,758
Do you still trust him?

26
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,721
Director Seo was framed too.

27
00:01:33,138 --> 00:01:35,140
Seo Yeong-woo just used you.

28
00:01:35,140 --> 00:01:36,933
And you fell for it.

29
00:01:37,058 --> 00:01:38,893
What do you know to talk such crap!

30
00:01:54,117 --> 00:01:55,618
Manager...

31
00:01:57,829 --> 00:01:58,913
Are you alright?

32
00:02:00,206 --> 00:02:01,082
Yeah...

33
00:02:02,876 --> 00:02:04,836
Oh dear, what should I do...

34
00:02:11,134 --> 00:02:12,719
I'm sorry.

35
00:02:16,306 --> 00:02:18,475
There should be some medicine around here.

36
00:02:28,943 --> 00:02:29,944
It's fine.

37
00:02:32,989 --> 00:02:34,491
Thanks.

38
00:02:35,909 --> 00:02:37,243
Manager...

39
00:02:37,619 --> 00:02:39,704
About the coffee you promised to buy me last time...

40
00:02:39,996 --> 00:02:41,748
Is that offer still valid?

41
00:02:43,875 --> 00:02:45,293
I have a meeting soon.

42
00:02:45,293 --> 00:02:46,461
Let's do it next time.

43
00:02:47,462 --> 00:02:48,463
Ah...

44
00:02:50,757 --> 00:02:51,674
Okay.

45
00:03:14,155 --> 00:03:16,449
The manager left this behind earlier.

46
00:03:18,535 --> 00:03:19,661
Really?

47
00:03:25,125 --> 00:03:27,127
Jihyeok, you're coming to the company dinner later too, right?

48
00:03:28,711 --> 00:03:30,380
Uh... the dinner?

49
00:03:32,006 --> 00:03:33,633
Is the manager coming too?

50
00:03:34,425 --> 00:03:37,470
Of course he is, it's a department dinner.

51
00:03:39,305 --> 00:03:40,306
Right?

52
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,683
Great, yeah.

53
00:03:55,905 --> 00:03:57,198
Jihyeok.

54
00:03:57,198 --> 00:03:58,199
Going to the restroom?

55
00:03:58,867 --> 00:03:59,784
No.

56
00:03:59,784 --> 00:04:01,369
I was waiting for you, Manager.

57
00:04:07,458 --> 00:04:09,419
Thanks for the coffee earlier.

58
00:04:11,796 --> 00:04:12,714
Thanks.

59
00:04:13,673 --> 00:04:15,717
You drank a lot today.

60
00:04:15,884 --> 00:04:17,010
You'll ruin your stomach.

61
00:04:18,553 --> 00:04:20,180
I'll go in first.

62
00:04:37,447 --> 00:04:39,407
What is this? Where did everyone go?

63
00:04:40,825 --> 00:04:42,243
The department head is paying for the second round

64
00:04:42,243 --> 00:04:44,495
so they went to the pub across the street.

65
00:04:45,205 --> 00:04:46,331
Oh, really?

66
00:04:47,582 --> 00:04:49,417
Then we should quickly follow...

67
00:04:49,417 --> 00:04:50,585
Manager...

68
00:04:51,461 --> 00:04:53,630
Manager, you're really drunk right now.

69
00:04:55,256 --> 00:04:56,674
I told everyone that I'd take care of you

70
00:04:56,674 --> 00:04:58,426
so...

71
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,930
We...

72
00:05:02,430 --> 00:05:04,140
Let's have just one more drink and then go.

73
00:05:18,446 --> 00:05:19,405
Manager...

74
00:05:19,948 --> 00:05:21,491
I heard the talk too.

75
00:05:22,784 --> 00:05:23,493
What?

76
00:05:25,578 --> 00:05:26,537
This whole thing...

77
00:05:27,038 --> 00:05:29,040
Was it really the director who ordered it?

78
00:05:30,708 --> 00:05:33,211
You just took the fall for him.

79
00:05:42,095 --> 00:05:44,180
Jihyeok, how long has it been since you joined?

80
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,182
Pardon?

81
00:05:50,395 --> 00:05:52,730
It's been three months for me.

82
00:05:55,525 --> 00:05:58,027
Don't let yourself get caught up in useless gossip.

83
00:05:59,946 --> 00:06:01,030
Ah...

84
00:06:01,656 --> 00:06:03,283
Yes, I'm sorry.

85
00:06:10,915 --> 00:06:11,916
I envy him.

86
00:06:15,837 --> 00:06:16,504
Ah...

87
00:06:16,504 --> 00:06:17,797
Oh, no...

88
00:06:17,797 --> 00:06:19,090
I mean, the director.

89
00:06:21,551 --> 00:06:23,386
Having a subordinate who trusts you like that,

90
00:06:23,386 --> 00:06:25,430
must be so reassuring.

91
00:06:34,522 --> 00:06:36,858
The director was a really good person.

92
00:06:39,235 --> 00:06:40,236
Really?

93
00:06:45,116 --> 00:06:47,035
If only it weren't for that accident...

94
00:06:56,502 --> 00:06:57,670
Manager...

95
00:07:01,007 --> 00:07:02,675
Are you okay?

96
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,816
If you want to cry, just cry.

97
00:07:18,816 --> 00:07:20,234
It's okay.

98
00:07:27,784 --> 00:07:28,993
Director...

99
00:07:30,953 --> 00:07:32,789
He will definitely return.

100
00:07:45,009 --> 00:07:46,094
Who is this?

101
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,470
Ah, Secretary Kim.

102
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:51,891
Here...

103
00:07:52,183 --> 00:07:53,434
Please take us here.

104
00:07:53,851 --> 00:07:54,644
Yes.

105
00:08:45,611 --> 00:08:47,113
Hyung...

106
00:08:50,032 --> 00:08:50,950
Seriously...

107
00:08:51,451 --> 00:08:52,660
Unbelievable.

108
00:09:08,176 --> 00:09:09,135
Manager...

109
00:09:10,511 --> 00:09:11,512
Manager?

110
00:09:18,352 --> 00:09:19,312
Yeongwoo hyung?
